// The files under this directory are illustrative documentation snippets, not
// part of Citadel's build. They reference hypothetical implementation packages
// (e.g. internal/ordering/...) that intentionally do not exist. Declaring a
// nested module here keeps them out of the root module's `go build ./...`,
// `go vet ./...`, and `go test ./...` so the examples never break the build.
module github.com/AymanKastali/citadel/docs/architecture/examples

go 1.26.4
